com.gotenna.sdk.commands

Interface GTCommandCenter.GTMessageListener

  • Enclosing class:
    GTCommandCenter

    public static interface GTCommandCenter.GTMessageListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when an incoming message is received from the goTenna.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onIncomingMessage(GTBaseMessageData baseMessageData)
      Called when a message is received that was be parsed into a goTenna SDK formatted message such as GTTextOnlyMessageData.
      void onIncomingMessage(GTMessageData messageData)
      Called when a message is received that COULD NOT be parsed into a goTenna SDK formatted message such as GTTextOnlyMessageData
